Introduction

Zhao Yue (simplified Chinese: 赵粤; traditional Chinese: 趙粵; pinyin: Zhào Yuè) is a Chinese idol singer.
She is a graduated member of Chinese idol group, SNH48 (Team NII), and active member of its sub-unit SEN7ES (also known as 7Senses).

She was also a member of Chinese project girl group Bonbon Girls 303, formed through the Chinese survival show Produce Camp 2020, where she placed 2nd.

Team History:
[2013.08.13] - Joined SNH48 as a Trainee.
[2013.11.11] - Promoted to SNH48 Team NII (Team NII formation).
[2017.04.07] - Joined SNH48 sub-unit 7SENSES.
[2020.07.14] - Placed 2nd on Produce Camp 2020, joined Bonbon Girls 303.
[2022.06.17] - Bonbon Girls 303 Disbandment.
[2022.07.04] - Returned to SNH48 Team NII.
[2022.07.04] - Returned to SNH48 SEN7ES.
[2022.09.11] - Graduated from SNH48 Team NII (Announcement: July 4, 2022 | Graduation Stage: September 11, 2022).
